      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "⑤ DerivedHousingFeatures — feature engineering (house_age, ratios, sale_month…)\n⑥ ColumnTransformer — StandardScaler + TargetEncoder (zipcode)\n⑦ XGBoost p50: log-previsão → expm1 → preço em USD\n⑧ XGBoost p10 / p90 → limites inferior e superior do intervalo",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⑤ DerivedHousingFeatures — feature engineering (house_age, ratios, sale_month…)\n⑥ ColumnTransformer — StandardScaler + TargetEncoder (zipcode)\n⑦ XGBoost p50: log-previsão → expm1 → preço em USD\n⑧ XGBoost p10 / p90 → limites inferior e superior do intervalo",
      "lineHeight": 1.45
